<div><span style="font-family: " palatino="" linotype";="" font-size:="" 18pt;"="">3dcart Installation Instructions</span></div>
<div><hr />
  <br />
  </div>
<div>What You Will Need:</div>
<div>
  <div>
    <ul>
      <li> A 3dcart Store with the 3dcart Blog enabled</li>
      <li>A Disqus Account</li>
    </ul>
    <div>Retrieving your Shortname</div></div></div>
<div>
  <ol>
    <li>Log into your Disqus account at www.disqus.com</li>
    <li>From the Disqus home page, click on your profile image and select <b>"Admin"</b></li>
    <li>Click on the <b>"Settings"</b> tab for the site you would like to retrieve the shortname for.</li>
    <li>On the <b>"Settings"</b> page, scroll down to <b>"Site Identity"</b> and your shortname will be listed for you. Save this information so that it can be added to your 3dcart store (see next section)</li>
  </ol>
  <div>Adding your Shortname to your 3dcart Store</div></div>
<div>
  <ol>
    <li>Log into your 3dcart Online Store Manager</li>
    <li>Go to Content - Blog</li>
    <li>Next, click on the "Blog Settings" button at the top right</li>
    <li>Place a mark in the "Use Disqus Comments" checkbox</li>
    <li>Enter your shortname in the <b>"Disqus Shortname"</b> field.</li>
    <li>Click Save Settings at the top right.</li>
  </ol>
  <div><a href="https://help.disqus.com/customer/portal/articles/1264625-getting-started">Continue to the getting started guide</a></div></div>
